{"version":1,"entries":{"person_1149952_translations":{"at":1773688717628,"data":{"id":1149952,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Bouwer Bosch","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ZA","iso_639_1":"af","name":"Afrikaans","english_name":"Afrikaans","data":{"biography":"","name":"Bouwer Bosch","primary":true}}]}},"person_34422_translations":{"at":1773688724872,"data":{"id":34422,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Francis Pierlot","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"ca","name":"Català","english_name":"Catalan","data":{"biography":"Francis Pierlot (Massachusetts, 15 de juliol de 1875 - Hollywood, Los Angeles, 11 de maig de 1955) va ser un actor teatral i cinematogràfic amb més de 90 crèdits cinematogràfics entre 1914 i 1953.","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_93803_translations":{"at":1773688726918,"data":{"id":93803,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Mamoru Miyano is a Japanese voice actor, actor, talent and singer. His agency is Himawari Theater Company, and releases his music under King Amusment Creative. He has also appeared as Prince Ismir in the stage production \"Crest of the Royal Family\" (王家の紋章 Ōke no monshō).","name":"Mamoru Miyano","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"　声優・俳優・歌手。\n\n　2001年に海外ドラマ「私はケイトリン」の吹き替えで声優デビュー。以降、「DEATH NOTE」や「機動戦士ガンダム00」など数多くの作品に出演するほか、映画「ファンタスティック・ビーストと魔法使いの旅」などで吹き替えを担当している。\n\n　また近年では俳優としても活動の場を広げており、グランドミュージカル「王家の紋章」ではイズミル役を、劇団☆新感線『髑髏城の七人』Season月《下弦の月》では主演・捨之介役を演じている。\n\n　アーティスト活動は2008年よりシングル「Discovery」でスタート。声優、俳優の現場で培った豊かな表現力と類い稀な歌声、そしてダンスを駆使した高いライブパフォーマンス力を武器に、独自のエンターテインメントを追求し続けている。","name":"宮野真守","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"日本男性声优、歌手，隶属于向日葵剧团，唱片公司为KING RECORDS。代表作品有《死亡笔记》夜神月、《樱兰高校男公关部》须王环、《机动战士高达00》刹那·F·清英、《吸血鬼骑士》锥生零、《STAR DRIVER 闪亮的塔科特》特纳西·塔科特、《无头骑士异闻录》纪田正臣、《命运石之门》冈部伦太郎、《歌之王子殿下》一之濑时矢、《花牌情缘》真岛太一、《Free!》松冈凛、《亚人》永井圭、《文豪野犬》太宰治等。2008年获得第二届声优奖主演男优奖。2012年获得第六届声优奖助演男优奖和歌唱奖（ST☆RISH名义）。2014年获的第八届声优奖歌唱奖（个人名义）。","name":"宫野真守","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"미야노 마모루","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","iso_639_1":"hi","name":"हिन्दी","english_name":"Hindi","data":{"biography":"","name":"मामोरू मियानो","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"宮野真守是日本的男性聲優、歌手、演員。出身於埼玉縣，所屬經紀公司為研音，所屬唱片公司為 King Records。","name":"宮野真守","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"מאמורו מיאנו","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"มาโมรุ มิยาโนะ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мамору Мияно","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мамору Міяно","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"مامورو ميانو","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IR","iso_639_1":"fa","name":"فارسی","english_name":"Persian","data":{"biography":"","name":"مامورو میانو","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mamoru Miyano","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mamoru Miyano","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mamoru Miyano","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Mamoru Miyano (宮野 真守, Miyano Mamoru, nacido el 8 de junio de 1983) es un actor de doblaje, actor, talento y cantante japonés de la prefectura de Saitama. Su agencia es la compañía de teatro Himawari y edita música bajo el sello King Amusement Creative.","name":"Mamoru Miyano","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mamoru Mijano","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mamoru Miyano","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BE","iso_639_1":"nl","name":"Nederlands","english_name":"Dutch","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"日本男性聲優、歌手，隸屬於向日葵劇團，唱片公司為 KING RECORDS。\n\n代表作品有《死亡筆記》夜神月、《櫻蘭高校男公關部》須王環、《機動戰士高達 00》剎那·F·清英、《吸血鬼騎士》錐生零、《STAR DRIVER 閃亮的塔科特》特納西·塔科特、《無頭騎士異聞錄》紀田正臣、《命運石之門》岡部倫太郎、《歌之王子殿下》一之瀨時矢、《花牌情緣》真島太一、《Free! 》松岡凜、《亞人》永井圭、《文豪野犬》太宰治等。\n\n2008 年獲得第二屆聲優獎主演男優獎。\n\n2012 年獲得第六屆聲優獎助演男優獎和歌唱獎（ST☆RISH 名義） 。\n\n2014 年獲的第八屆聲優獎歌唱獎（個人名義）。","name":"宮野真守","primary":false}}]}},"person_2027680_translations":{"at":1773688727238,"data":{"id":2027680,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Fang Wenqiang","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"方文强，演员。 2014年，出演青春剧《匆匆那年》，剧中饰演王森昭。2016年，出演青春剧《最好的我们》，剧中饰演张平老师。","name":"方文强","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Fang Wenqiang","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"方文強，演員。\n\n2014 年，出演青春劇《匆匆那年》，劇中飾演王森昭。2016 年，出演青春劇《最好的我們》，劇中飾演張平老師。","name":"方文強","primary":false}}]}},"person_2317989_translations":{"at":1773688728372,"data":{"id":2317989,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lu Yanqi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陆妍淇，1月15日出生于安徽省淮南市，中国内地女演员，毕业于解放军艺术学院舞蹈系。\n\n2015年，因出演家庭情感剧《搭错车》而正式进入影视圈 。同年，凭借在芒果TV自制剧《女生日记之做决定事务所》中饰演江小夏一角受到关注。\n\n2016年，出演浪漫年代剧《翡翠恋人》；随后，主演三国题材古装剧《大军师司马懿之军师联盟》。2017年，主演跨次元校园偶像剧《班长大人》。\n\n2018年，与刘昊然、宋祖儿等人合作出演英雄史诗剧《九州缥缈录》，与菅纫姿、张博等人合作主演都市情景剧《天才管家》，与罗晋、李一桐等人合作出演《鹤唳华亭》。","name":"陆妍淇","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陸妍淇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"Lục Nghiên Kỳ, sinh ngày 15 tháng 1 năm 1992 tại thành phố Hoài Nam, tỉnh An Huy, tốt nghiệp Khoa Múa của Học viện Nghệ thuật Giải phóng Quân, là nữ diễn viên Trung Quốc đại lục.","name":"Lục Nghiên Kỳ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陸妍淇，1 月 15 日出生於安徽省淮南市，中國內地女演員，畢業於解放軍藝術學院舞蹈系。\n\n2015 年，因出演家庭情感劇《搭錯車》而正式進入影視圈 。同年，憑借在芒果 TV 自制劇《女生日記之做決定事務所》中飾演江小夏一角受到關注。\n\n2016 年，出演浪漫年代劇《翡翠戀人》；隨後，主演三國題材古裝劇《大軍師司馬懿之軍師聯盟》。2017 年，主演跨次元校園偶像劇《班長大人》。\n\n2018 年，與劉昊然、宋祖兒等人合作出演英雄史詩劇《九州縹緲錄》，與菅紉姿、張博等人合作主演都市情景劇《天才管家》，與羅晉、李一桐等人合作出演《鶴唳華亭》。","name":"陸妍淇","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1319972_keywords":{"at":1773688728602,"data":{"id":1319972,"keywords":[]}},"movie_1289936_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1773688729143,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/jvzPTf0nhsqAXodYT6ILKb99IA2.jpg","belongs_to_collection":{"id":925006,"name":"Loạt phim Downton Abbey","poster_path":"/d7WcrOsGWkJYAgaZWy00luZBcjf.jpg","backdrop_path":"/ibqyhoVh0RD5DI2jgnvvFcrJYV7.jpg"},"budget":50000000,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"},{"id":10749,"name":"Phim Lãng Mạn"}],"homepage":"","id":1289936,"imdb_id":"tt31888477","origin_country":["GB","US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Downton Abbey: The Grand Finale","overview":"Khi Mary rơi vào tâm điểm của một vụ bê bối gây chấn động dư luận và gia đình đối mặt với khủng hoảng tài chính, cả dinh thự Crawley phải gồng mình trước nguy cơ mất danh dự và địa vị xã hội. Giữa thời khắc chuyển giao, những người thừa kế và tầng lớp phục vụ buộc phải thích nghi với thời đại mới – nơi truyền thống, quyền lực và tình thân đều bị thử thách. Một chương mới đang mở ra cho Downton Abbey, khi thế hệ kế tiếp đứng lên dẫn dắt ngôi nhà biểu tượng này bước vào tương lai.","popularity":5.8846,"poster_path":"/m1tLlMTCwc6oK6OjWTOI4b32wnA.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":6196,"logo_path":"/nTHxXVnXL58M7jJGNFAjRTCRgyg.png","name":"Carnival Films","origin_country":"GB"},{"id":10146,"logo_path":"/xnFIOeq5cKw09kCWqV7foWDe4AA.png","name":"Focus Features","origin_country":"US"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"GB","name":"United Kingdom"},{"iso_3166_1":"US","name":"United States of America"}],"release_date":"2025-09-10","revenue":102925647,"runtime":123,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Dinh Thự Downton: Hồi Kết Huy Hoàng","video":false,"vote_average":7.092,"vote_count":228}},"person_2281921_translations":{"at":1773688734476,"data":{"id":2281921,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Sally Amaki (天城サリー, born April 26 2000) is an American singer and voice actress based in Tokyo, Japan. She is a member of the voice acting idol group 22/7 which debuted in 2017, and is the group's \"overseas representative.\" Within the group, she appears both as herself and as the animated